        "html": "<h2 style=\"color:#1f365c; font-size:28px; font-weight:700; border-bottom:2px solid #c9a040; padding-bottom:10px; margin:0 0 16px;\">Your Path</h2>\n<p style=\"color:#444; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6; margin:0 0 28px;\">Two tiers. Start free, or activate the full platform with Five Star Alliance.</p>\n\n<!-- TIER 1: FREE -->\n<div style=\"background:#fff; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-top:4px solid #888; border-radius:4px; padding:24px 24px; margin-bottom:20px;\">\n  <div style=\"display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:baseline; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:10px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"color:#1f365c; font-size:22px; font-weight:700; margin:0;\">Start Free</h3>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:600; color:#888; margin:0;\">Free</p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:12px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 14px;\">No Membership Required</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#444; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; margin:0 0 18px;\">Cash offer aggregation on every property in the country. Every signup gets an auto-provisioned hosted page. The simplest way to experience the platform.</p>\n  <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:10px;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:12px 14px; background:#f7f7f5; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-radius:4px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#1f365c; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">Cash Offers</p>\n      <p style=\"font-size:13px; color:#666; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Unlimited addresses. Real, competitive offers from active institutional buyers.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:12px 14px; background:#f7f7f5; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-radius:4px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#1f365c; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">Hosted Page</p>\n      <p style=\"font-size:13px; color:#666; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Auto-provisioned your-name.fsioffers.com subdomain. Live in minutes.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;\"><a href=\"https://fsioffers.com\" style=\"color:#1f365c; font-weight:600; font-size:14px; text-decoration:none; border-bottom:2px solid #c9a040; padding-bottom:2px;\">Create your free account &rarr;</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<!-- TIER 2: ALLIANCE -->\n<div style=\"background:#1f365c; color:#fff; border-radius:6px; padding:28px 28px; margin-bottom:8px;\">\n  <div style=\"display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:baseline; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:10px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"color:#fff; font-size:22px; font-weight:700; margin:0;\">Five Star Alliance</h3>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:600; color:#c9a040; margin:0;\">$495 per year</p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:12px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 14px;\">FSI's Universal Membership &middot; Full Platform Access</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#cfd5de; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; margin:0 0 18px;\">Alliance unlocks the entire FSI Offers platform and is the entry point for every professional in the Five Star Institute community. The floor that every community-specific FSI membership builds on.</p>\n  <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:10px; margin:0 0 16px;\">\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">15 Leads per Month</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Fully enriched website visitor identification. Names, contacts, property data, equity estimates.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">Full Platform Suite</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Skip trace, marketing pages, landing page builder, CRM automation, website widgets.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">Hosted Website</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">your-name.fsioffers.com included. Optional custom domain, self-serve setup.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">Overage Leads</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">$8 per enriched lead beyond your monthly allocation.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;\"><a href=\"mailto:membership@thefivestar.com\" style=\"color:#c9a040; font-weight:600; font-size:14px;\">Contact us about Five Star Alliance &rarr;</a></p>\n</div>"
      },
